A [[MTA]] or [[Mail Transfer Agent]] (sometimes also [[Mail Transport Agent]]) is a program that transfers [[mail]] from one computer to another over a network using a protocol like [[SMTP]]. [[Sendmail]] is an example of a popular MTA.

